Test Results:
- 5/7 agents passing (71.4% success rate)
- Metrics dashboard operational with real-time updates
- System health score calculation working

Technical Changes:
- Modified AgentCommunicationLogger to use localStorage as backing store
- Added loadFromStorage() and saveToStorage() methods
- Updated clearLogs() to also clear localStorage
- Created test interfaces for agent validation

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
